[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Reviewing naming conventions**\n\nI'm considering the rule about not using $ in test class or file names, but it seems there are existing instances where $ is used. I find this a bit confusing! It makes me think about specific components, like the IsolatedClassLoader in XML4J, which seems to have a child-first approach with org.jdom and org.apache.xerces.parsers. I wonder if these existing uses create any inconsistencies or potential issues in the codebase. It’s definitely something to keep an eye on!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_04d3a5750ac2288e0169fc839aaad481978bf5cbcce4b34d6b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp_IOkmhe0mo7tAQojOJM4u_VTv3t5X13MwCJ8fiOxDjAnDPxL3w4GHfulxYDIanLw5l9TawDW60_s8Ls6f2BWz5jzbSRf10z2Jmz6ewiCzV_3vwo7fcVMR0bkq1Ih6AWvMKWynb_TasKCAPhPNnUsr-8eTEwpIZdawazwaQ104_YxxrTg5KAmo7HihhnxLDnqG2x-EnafLNPx0kmzC4KtNVV7rFoPuLxPvgV1II_Sf3HlynXdXcjHG7Z5y9l5ktZvxhDdWpv6aMKQB7xVzu2mm7x1C_CI-ZZOGrxe_KpXl_6f2roCsE-7r-aYX9FxdbJKOMBSNYJahXjXQYrzxDxcdmjPSXfPMGQDM7hV_Cekn_agG37wTEZypI-j4v-5oVfzwIU-FCPcGfKUdxR8RzFyjxZjtAv1bgdS8RNpv3RTDfC5I-ZgstZ5DvSvI-CgllIfrm_0a5y05QlMqRnCcMLn4V6-OXw3fKVrTZqH3rSlX8Wf0W5Va-Bp3MCsSOoAVlX1geQ39fI-mumhp1i213Fc2rHn3MTtuYGqAjUc9T_PYiv0-XUG70z96cBTIH6D2wf67nlLy1QSzQErGZ5tYPle19tPsDXfURWgqO5XnvW2wHWki-WFHq5uyacbb6j_jcy6UfgeYyxh3jk3ofT7S77ljRHWHuopoauTOmerby_QWh4DWllQQHm1b2kKcIaUx6JzLLQYAiPK6-lFtVu4yUwyXCH-6K7KX6C55EZ47JNcO5Jp6kdZqLizaTGo4Mz-ZYDGkwLVvQpMwKWsksEjOlQ0SoT44JoSTK6xfbCm5VxVmy8JEL8JfSVKZAUgU_PpdHsjz4QiBuTBz5ItFZOa8qaHSdNxG7n4YF28PGl3nUjlG-oL6SmfqBOO2zZTH7K2qQ1-s1twr2TPCATyP3BaAv_o5Ns39V-Bd6EsxWtmaGdLnW-fVz-xn8TCMmyxBSEMTmEVQY1zsuUO8td8k2Aene4RumU_CPCiOcFhJaONpR98yg5lYcq53suF0Dq9jPaZPO64sr-t501Sh-pRfQ0QxQiAMMqIUXnI_HeZxqPeAGYgDvnA3jDhk71rq6KIFFV8HXIQajeBYcrpBFb6q5pDBzkDa5QGu9AVbN1p3PHuF3fu9BAkXuCFnx3TKr0oNaQxApyJqChDnTqWb-djL0a1m11mtlT7dsXi0vUf5hiYepTZNBU98reehzxe6TT1z-V49ycmB7bC1T3f562RjfhhemrzrGl